{{speciesbox|name=''Mecyclothorax ferruginiosus''|genus=Mecyclothorax|authority=Perrault, 1987}}
'''''Mecyclothorax ferruginiosus''''' is a species of [[ground beetle]] in the subfamily [[Psydrinae]].<ref name="carabidae">{{cite web |url=http://carabidae.org/carabidae/mecyclothorax-sharp-1903.html |title=''Mecyclothorax'' Sharp, 1903 |year=2011 |work=Carabidae of the World |accessdate=7 August 2013}}</ref> It was described by Perrault in 1987.<ref name="carabidae"/>

